name: Michael Waltman
text: Great experience and an even better staff

name: Ivy Sundberg
text: The instructors are really nice. No matter how much my son threw a fit they were really nice and helped him with his lesson.

name: Carl Myrick
text: The coaches are amazing. Wonderful experience.

name: Paul Miller
text: Great training facility. Wheel chair accessible. Also Team River Runner trains in the pool with kayaks.

name: William Shields
text: Good coaching for adult swimming too

name: Barbara De Zutter
text: The facilities could use an upgrade. Only used by Swat swimming club
